QuestData.Title: Work Order: Kirin Tor Offensive I
QuestData.Description: <Yoon keeps the details of this order short, but detailed.>$b$bAnother request has come through for the Alliance. The Kirin Tor Offensive, located out on the Isle of Thunder, has requested a bushel of juicycrunch carrots.$b$bThough this Horde and Alliance conflict still gets my fur in a bristle, I won't turn away a hungry stomach.
QuestData.LogDescription: Plant 8 Juicycrunch Carrot Seeds on Sunsong Ranch.
